### Login Admin — gera novo token
# @name login
POST http://localhost:3001/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@maissaudebr.com",
  "password": "senha123"
}

###

@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### Teste 1 - Health check
GET http://localhost:3001/health


### Teste 2 - Registrar usuario admin
POST http://localhost:3001/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Marcos Admin",
  "email": "admin@maissaudebr.com",
  "password": "senha123",
  "role": "ADMIN"
}


### Teste 3 - Login (captura o token)
# @name login
POST http://localhost:3001/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@maissaudebr.com",
  "password": "senha123"
}


### Teste 4 - Listar appointments (autenticado)
GET http://localhost:3001/appointments
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}
### Teste 5 - Criar paciente
# @name novoPaciente
POST http://localhost:3002/patients/bulk-import
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="pacientes.xlsx"
Content-Type: application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet

< ./pacientes.xlsx
------WebKitFormBoundary--

{
  "name": "Joao da Silva",
  "cpf": "12345678901",
  "email": "joao@example.com",
  "phone": "11999998888",
  "birthDate": "1985-03-15",
  "gender": "M"
}


### Teste 6 - Listar pacientes
GET http://localhost:3001/patients
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}
### Teste 7 - Criar medico (cria User + Doctor numa transacao)
# @name novoMedico
POST http://localhost:3001/doctors
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Dra. Ana Souza",
  "email": "ana.souza@maissaudebr.com",
  "password": "senha123",
  "crm": "CRM-SP-123456",
  "specialty": "Cardiologia",
  "consultPrice": 350.00,
  "consultTime": 30
}


### Teste 8 - Listar medicos
GET http://localhost:3001/doctors
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

### Teste 9 - Criar appointment (agendar consulta)
# @name novaConsulta
POST http://localhost:3001/appointments
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patientId": "30b993f7-0627-4b80-bbdb-5bcf953a3c91",
  "doctorId": "34b6187e-5bb7-4c92-9825-974c9abfd59a",
  "scheduledAt": "2026-05-15T14:00:00Z",
  "duration": 30,
  "notes": "Primeira consulta - avaliacao cardiologica"
}


### Teste 10 - Listar appointments (deve mostrar a consulta criada)
GET http://localhost:3001/appointments
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}


### Teste 11 - Tentar criar OUTRA consulta no MESMO horario (deve dar 409)
POST http://localhost:3001/appointments
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patientId": "30b993f7-0627-4b80-bbdb-5bcf953a3c91",
  "doctorId": "34b6187e-5bb7-4c92-9825-974c9abfd59a",
  "scheduledAt": "2026-05-15T14:15:00Z",
  "duration": 30,
  "notes": "Tentativa de conflito - deve falhar"
}

### Teste 12 - Buscar appointment por ID
GET http://localhost:3001/appointments/fe0ee36a-00d7-4a42-8686-19c01950e7b1
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}


### Teste 13 - PATCH: confirmar a consulta (mudar status para CONFIRMED)
PATCH http://localhost:3001/appointments/fe0ee36a-00d7-4a42-8686-19c01950e7b1
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "CONFIRMED"
}


### Teste 14 - PATCH: reagendar para outro horario (deve passar - sem conflito)
PATCH http://localhost:3001/appointments/fe0ee36a-00d7-4a42-8686-19c01950e7b1
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "scheduledAt": "2026-05-15T16:00:00Z",
  "notes": "Reagendado a pedido do paciente"
}


### Teste 15 - DELETE: cancelar consulta (soft delete via status)
DELETE http://localhost:3001/appointments/fe0ee36a-00d7-4a42-8686-19c01950e7b1
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}


### Teste 16 - Listar appointments depois do cancelamento
GET http://localhost:3001/appointments
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

### ==============================
### PAYMENTS — Sub-etapa 2.1
### ==============================

### 1) Pagamento avulso (sem appointment) — DEVE retornar 201
POST http://localhost:3001/payments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "patientId": "30b993f7-0627-4b80-bbdb-5bcf953a3c91",
  "amount": 150.00,
  "method": "PIX"
}

### 2) Pagamento avulso JÁ PAGO — paidAt deve ser preenchido automaticamente
POST http://localhost:3001/payments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "patientId": "30b993f7-0627-4b80-bbdb-5bcf953a3c91",
  "amount": 80.00,
  "method": "DEBIT_CARD",
  "status": "PAID"
}

### 3) Paciente inexistente — DEVE retornar 404 PATIENT_NOT_FOUND
POST http://localhost:3001/payments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "patientId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "amount": 100,
  "method": "PIX"
}

### 4) Validação Zod — amount negativo DEVE retornar 400
POST http://localhost:3001/payments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "patientId": "30b993f7-0627-4b80-bbdb-5bcf953a3c91",
  "amount": -10,
  "method": "PIX"
}

### 5) Sem token — DEVE retornar 401
POST http://localhost:3001/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patientId": "30b993f7-0627-4b80-bbdb-5bcf953a3c91",
  "amount": 100,
  "method": "PIX"
}

### 6) Criar novo appointment para o teste 7
POST http://localhost:3001/appointments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "patientId": "30b993f7-0627-4b80-bbdb-5bcf953a3c91",
  "doctorId": "34b6187e-5bb7-4c92-9825-974c9abfd59a",
  "scheduledAt": "2025-12-10T14:00:00.000Z",
  "durationMinutes": 30
}

### 7) Pagamento vinculado ao appointment criado em (6)
POST http://localhost:3001/payments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "patientId": "30b993f7-0627-4b80-bbdb-5bcf953a3c91",
  "appointmentId": "316cb984-a576-4c7a-9f3a-89c14f490e38",
  "amount": 350.00,
  "method": "CREDIT_CARD",
  "status": "PAID"
}

### 8) Tentar criar OUTRO pagamento para o MESMO appointment — DEVE retornar 409
POST http://localhost:3001/payments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "patientId": "30b993f7-0627-4b80-bbdb-5bcf953a3c91",
  "appointmentId": "316cb984-a576-4c7a-9f3a-89c14f490e38",
  "amount": 350.00,
  "method": "PIX"
}

### 9) Pagamento com paciente errado para o appointment — DEVE retornar 400 APPOINTMENT_PATIENT_MISMATCH
### (use um patientId DIFERENTE do dono do appointment de (6))
### Crie outro paciente antes se ainda não tiver, ou pule este teste por agora.

### ==============================
### PAYMENTS — Sub-etapa 2.2 (GET /payments)
### ==============================

### 1) Listar todos (paginação default: page=1, pageSize=20)
GET http://localhost:3001/payments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2) Filtrar por status PAID
GET http://localhost:3001/payments?status=PAID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3) Filtrar por método PIX
GET http://localhost:3001/payments?method=PIX
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4) Filtrar por paciente (João da Silva)
GET http://localhost:3001/payments?patientId=30b993f7-0627-4b80-bbdb-5bcf953a3c91
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5) Filtrar por período (createdAt nos últimos 30 dias)
### Ajuste as datas conforme hoje
GET http://localhost:3001/payments?from=2026-04-01T00:00:00.000Z&to=2026-05-01T23:59:59.000Z
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6) Filtrar por período usando paidAt (caixa)
GET http://localhost:3001/payments?from=2026-04-01T00:00:00.000Z&to=2026-05-01T23:59:59.000Z&dateField=paidAt
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7) Combinar filtros: PAID + PIX
GET http://localhost:3001/payments?status=PAID&method=PIX
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8) Paginação: pageSize=2 (forçar mais de 1 página)
GET http://localhost:3001/payments?page=1&pageSize=2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9) Página 2 com pageSize=2
GET http://localhost:3001/payments?page=2&pageSize=2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10) Validação Zod — pageSize maior que 100 DEVE retornar 400
GET http://localhost:3001/payments?pageSize=500
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11) Validação Zod — patientId não-UUID DEVE retornar 400
GET http://localhost:3001/payments?patientId=abc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12) Sem token DEVE retornar 401
GET http://localhost:3001/payments

### ==============================
### PAYMENTS — Sub-etapa 2.3 (GET /payments/summary)
### ==============================

### 1) Summary geral (sem filtros) — usa paidAt como default
GET http://localhost:3001/payments/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2) Summary por createdAt (vê todos os 4 pagamentos criados)
GET http://localhost:3001/payments/summary?dateField=createdAt
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3) Summary com período (ajuste as datas conforme hoje)
GET http://localhost:3001/payments/summary?from=2026-04-01T00:00:00.000Z&to=2026-05-31T23:59:59.000Z&dateField=createdAt
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4) Summary de um paciente específico
GET http://localhost:3001/payments/summary?patientId=30b993f7-0627-4b80-bbdb-5bcf953a3c91&dateField=createdAt
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5) Summary com período fora dos dados — totais devem ser 0
GET http://localhost:3001/payments/summary?from=2020-01-01T00:00:00.000Z&to=2020-12-31T23:59:59.000Z&dateField=createdAt
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6) Validação Zod — patientId não-UUID DEVE retornar 400
GET http://localhost:3001/payments/summary?patientId=abc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7) Validação Zod — dateField inválido DEVE retornar 400
GET http://localhost:3001/payments/summary?dateField=invalido
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8) Sem token DEVE retornar 401
GET http://localhost:3001/payments/summary